{"tid":1894692,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［推到事主出黎道歉］無腦港女菠蘿山懸崖抱貓打卡","createTime":"2020-02-24T05:37:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T06:29:32.000Z","uid":200580,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4d554ded3f72d0cec99187ec0f3c0a6ea184bc83","tid":1894692,"uid":200580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:37:32.000Z","msg":"話說我上星期五同朋友行菠蘿山 <br />\n行到大峽谷嗰個打卡位<br />\n見到有個港女企喺條好窄嘅崖邊位影相<br />\n本身都以為冇乜野 望真啲先見到佢抱住隻貓仲要舉高佢<br />\n可能佢以為自己係lion king入面隻狒狒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我成程望住條女 佢明知隻貓好驚，掙扎緊 <br />\n但佢冇即時抱返佢落嚟又或者停止影相 行返上大路到<br />\n而係繼續影埋佢啲打卡相先<br />\n最後影完相準備行返出去嗰陣 隻貓已經勁驚、唔受控<br />\n佢要將隻貓塞落件衫入面先帶到佢出嚟 <br />\n<br />\n同埋成個過程(大約20分鐘左右) 佢都冇為隻貓做任何安全措施 e.g. 頸帶嗰啲 <br />\n萬一貓貓真係跌咗落去 我諗呢條無腦港女都唔會爬落去救佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港女抱貓圖 (對唔住冇高清 因為個刻望到已經好驚同擔心隻貓)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EURcV7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEURcV7d.jpg&h=378c68d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eoJVTTV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeoJVTTV.png&h=4f89d616&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n打卡嗰個位<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/twJyFyV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtwJyFyV.jpg&h=622c3995&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4967cadcc0984e860f48ba36b2a59d85eb6af4b","tid":1894692,"uid":39710,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:38:24.000Z","msg":"呢排好多癡撚線嘅人行山"},{"pid":"7f5673933357a9c7df0b6a35ec344dd74438b426","tid":1894692,"uid":159916,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:39:35.000Z","msg":"係你就直接同佢講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兜咁大個圈隻貓死左九次啦"},{"pid":"a5b7853b3139495b1d07dd64d9900d914a5797c4","tid":1894692,"uid":36435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:39:50.000Z","msg":"Ok網路公審"},{"pid":"865e674e4e8d39010c71785dcd1b3f4db06f3dca","tid":1894692,"uid":31920,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:40:10.000Z","msg":"帶貓行山都要比人批鬥<br />\n<br />\n痴撚線"},{"pid":"3c7f1b6956190c52c4544ddc6dbf35526a8b8267","tid":1894692,"uid":315073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:40:13.000Z","msg":"個條路我自己一個人行都驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要抱住隻貓<br />\n消防真係多得呢啲人唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f6721a752adf32f898a24819ae6c6f19ab16d8","tid":1894692,"uid":315073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"865e674e4e8d39010c71785dcd1b3f4db06f3dca","tid":1894692,"uid":31920,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:40:10.000Z","msg":"帶貓行山都要比人批鬥<br />\n<br />\n痴撚線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:40:51.000Z","msg":"ching你睇清楚未，懸崖黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e457397f04d3518e72eaf00e41d7d186caa9c2","tid":1894692,"uid":124252,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:41:30.000Z","msg":"以為自己係lion king入面隻狒狒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"502c683ecd9281aa9ee81bcc1bcba7c540b7c829","tid":1894692,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:41:58.000Z","msg":"點解個界面怪怪地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42fc449ba7906ed996d7fc8b2ec6363228111e0d","tid":1894692,"uid":40131,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:42:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba035